Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.91,0:03:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}前半還好 後半已經跟管樂沒關係了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.21,0:03:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}再說大五郎是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.24,0:03:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我家小狗的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.14,0:03:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大家認真點想啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.50,0:03:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.53,0:03:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}而且還全都寫下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.93,0:03:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}話說 我希望隊名有個性…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.15,0:03:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}「只有這10人才有的」那樣的！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.89,0:03:44.57,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大五郎超有個性的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.64,0:03:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}個性…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.84,0:03:46.69,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}人又跑哪去了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.81,0:03:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}把大家名字的首字串起來如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.36,0:03:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就這個！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.42,0:03:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}Yo ka hi fu mo na ta ka na ka
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.64,0:03:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好長
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.81,0:03:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.71,0:04:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}而且也串不起來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.96,0:04:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}把學姐的首字串起來如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.53,0:04:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那就是…二年級的中川夏紀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.06,0:04:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}森田忍 還有我壁友枝…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.93,0:04:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.90,0:04:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}Namoka…Kamo…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.50,0:04:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}Monaka…？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.35,0:04:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}莫娜卡！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.21,0:04:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不錯啊 莫娜卡隊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.62,0:04:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}聽起來很可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.31,0:04:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哎…怎麼好像諧星團體
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.69,0:04:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}王國…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.38,0:04:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那是摩納哥公國 況且也不是王國
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.11,0:04:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我覺得可愛是很重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.09,0:04:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.79,0:04:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}反正也就用到大賽結束
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.70,0:04:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那我們的隊名就…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.76,0:04:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}決定為莫娜卡隊了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.11,0:04:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哎…莫娜卡？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.20,0:04:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}為什麼叫莫娜卡？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.67,0:04:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.88,0:04:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}Monaka…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.68,0:04:51.43,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}※日語Monaka有好時辰、最火熱的時候之意
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.47,0:04:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}「我們正值花樣年華時！」這樣的？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.66,0:04:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不是 只是把二年級的姓名首字串了起來…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.56,0:05:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好簡單！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.63,0:05:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒什麼關係吧 反正也好記
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.13,0:05:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我覺得這名字很不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.40,0:05:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}也是可以啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.46,0:05:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那再對大家說兩句吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.28,0:05:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}啊…好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.01,0:05:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我們莫娜卡隊 今後將會和各位一起朝著大賽努力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.06,0:05:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}有什麼能幫得上忙的 請告訴我們
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.34,0:05:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}莫名地緊張啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.92,0:05:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯 我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.73,0:05:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不過沒辦法參與合奏練習
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.21,0:05:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}落選的感覺就變得好真實
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.58,0:05:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}瀧老師也叫我們把悔恨投入練習中啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.14,0:05:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.37,0:05:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}而且我們明年還有機會的 所以先練習吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.08,0:05:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.34,0:05:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好 Fight 莫娜卡！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.74,0:05:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.90,0:05:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}感覺不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.12,0:05:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}對吧～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.54,0:06:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}卓柏…卡布拉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.88,0:06:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}葉月 我們在二樓練習
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.85,0:06:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.95,0:06:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}還有誰沒通知的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.61,0:06:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.52,0:06:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}一鼓作氣！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.69,0:06:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}練…練習呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.49,0:06:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}現在是休息時間
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.13,0:06:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.50,0:06:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我來幫你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.04,0:06:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不用啦 有輪子呢 你看
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.93,0:06:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.75,0:06:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}下完樓梯就輕鬆了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.94,0:06:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那就幫你到下樓吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.71,0:06:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}可以…幫我搬著下面嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.09,0:06:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.46,0:07:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}可以囉 鬆開手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.14,0:07:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.37,0:07:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好重！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.40,0:07:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這要一個人搬也太累了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.52,0:07:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我已經習慣了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.97,0:07:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}記得你是高中才加入管樂社的？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.02,0:07:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}之前告訴你了啊 沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.17,0:07:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.73,0:07:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}說起來…我問過你為什麼要選低音號嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.59,0:07:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.19,0:07:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}其實一開始想選小號的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.91,0:07:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但被明日香學姐騙了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.32,0:07:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}什麼…被騙？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.76,0:07:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯 她說「這是你命中的另一半」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.18,0:07:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}塚本一直都是吹長號？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.59,0:07:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒有 國中時是吹法國號
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.61,0:07:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是嗎 但你長號居然吹得這麼好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.33,0:08:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}因為以前就一直想吹長號
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.86,0:08:06.52,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\bord1\1c&HD2D7CD&\3c&H36413A&\frz19.13\move(462,268,356,266,0,7626)}那邊的你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.86,0:08:06.52,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\bord1\3c&H36413A&\frz15.37\move(624,428,518,424,0,7626)}{\1c&HB1905F&}青{\1c&H9FB7E9&}春
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.86,0:08:06.52,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\bord1\1c&H3AA6D4&\3c&H36413A&\frz15.61\move(682,572,576,570,0,7626)}就是管樂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.46,0:08:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我喜歡爵士長號
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.98,0:08:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.42,0:08:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.60,0:08:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.46,0:08:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.98,0:08:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒什麼 那我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.32,0:08:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.44,0:08:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}塚本
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.35,0:08:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.64,0:08:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒事的！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.82,0:08:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}加藤…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.73,0:08:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你練習加油
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.56,0:08:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那久美子現在怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.97,0:08:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}久美子？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.46,0:08:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.42,0:08:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我們練習是分開的嘛 不怎麼能常在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.88,0:09:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}普普通通吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.68,0:09:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但自選曲裡她有地方還不太熟…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.61,0:09:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不…我不是這意思
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.32,0:09:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你想 合奏的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.70,0:09:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}塚本就在她身邊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.60,0:09:15.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以怎麼說呢…我有點在意
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.14,0:09:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}難道葉月你要…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.44,0:09:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}搶老公？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.82,0:09:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不是不是不是！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.32,0:09:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒關係 實話實說吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.61,0:09:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}都說不是了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.89,0:09:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不要緊的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.31,0:09:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}喜歡什麼人是自由的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.06,0:09:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}綠輝…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.17,0:09:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是小綠
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.10,0:09:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}手刀！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.85,0:09:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}搞什麼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.09,0:09:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不是…不是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.50,0:09:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要是因為我害他們變得很僵
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.35,0:09:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我也不好受
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.96,0:09:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但我如果亂插嘴 事情可能會更複雜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.24,0:09:59.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我就是不擅長這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.79,0:10:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎麼說呢…以前還覺得戀愛很麻煩呀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.36,0:10:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真的是…很麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.76,0:10:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}心情莫名其妙的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.36,0:10:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要是沒告白就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.67,0:10:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}才沒…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.77,0:10:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}手刀！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.18,0:10:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}搞什麼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.39,0:10:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}才沒這回事！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.08,0:10:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}比什麼都不做好太多了！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.39,0:10:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}葉月很棒 很帥氣 超可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.81,0:10:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}走吧 去便利商店
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.63,0:10:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}等…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.46,0:10:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}又要玩樂器轉蛋？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.85,0:10:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不是 我請客
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.83,0:10:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哎 真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.97,0:10:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.29,0:10:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那買貴一點的冰淇淋？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.40,0:10:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.16,0:10:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}護身符？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.90,0:11:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}把我們的心意藏在裡面 送給參賽成員
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.45,0:11:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我在電視上看到過
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.51,0:11:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要親手做嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.78,0:11:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯 還在考慮要什麼樣的吉祥物
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.45,0:11:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}做50多個是不是太辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.25,0:11:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大家分擔一下就好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.55,0:11:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}拉拉想做可愛的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.70,0:11:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}像是蟬？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.59,0:11:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哪裡可愛了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.77,0:11:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那還是根據我們的隊名…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.54,0:11:22.41,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}※Monaka還有另個意思，指用糯米粉烤成的皮中間夾著紅豆沙的一種和點心。\N\h\h\h\h之後桌上的紙片是夾在飾品中的幸運籤。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.88,0:11:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}看 怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.51,0:11:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}做得真好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.66,0:11:28.53,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}也教教拉拉技巧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.83,0:11:29.24,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.37,0:11:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}他們會發現嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.72,0:11:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就是要那種感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.81,0:11:34.52,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}謝謝 這樣呀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.97,0:11:35.88,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.16,0:11:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這什麼啊 好大！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.79,0:11:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好熱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.48,0:11:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}落選時還以為練習會輕鬆點…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.81,0:11:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.68,0:11:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我覺得還是忙一點好 閒著反而很寂寞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.24,0:12:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}也是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.69,0:12:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}說吧 剛剛偷走了誰的籤？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.83,0:12:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}誰的誰的？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.24,0:12:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.53,0:12:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是嗎 看錯了嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.39,0:12:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.32,0:12:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.06,0:12:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}夏樹學姐有沒有和男生交往過
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.81,0:12:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}保密
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.03,0:12:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}也是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.65,0:12:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}長號…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.48,0:12:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}還有上低音號
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.89,0:12:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}應該是久美子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.54,0:12:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哎 突然怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.48,0:12:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}雖然搞不太懂 就是想疼愛你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.02,0:12:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}為什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.73,0:12:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}都說了不知道嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.03,0:12:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}很熱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.80,0:13:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}乖 乖
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.17,0:13:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不過
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.74,0:13:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}可不要讓自己後悔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.28,0:13:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我也只能說這句
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.07,0:13:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.61,0:13:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我還是覺得…能進低音聲部真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.53,0:13:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.98,0:13:33.02,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\bord0\fs45\3c&HFFFFFF&\c&H000000&\pos(896,176)}指揮
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.98,0:13:33.02,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\c&HBDA40F&\3c&HFFFFFF&\fs45\pos(889,171)}指揮
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.24,0:13:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}天亮啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.34,0:14:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}早安
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.02,0:14:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}早
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.93,0:14:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}早
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.11,0:14:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你們來得真早
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.47,0:14:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你也是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.50,0:14:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那各自仔細收拾行李
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.05,0:14:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}跟昨天的一起放到走廊上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.12,0:14:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.14,0:14:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}葉月 早啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.69,0:14:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哦 久美子 高坂同學 早啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.46,0:14:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}早
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.39,0:14:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}來得真早
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.50,0:14:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}喔 兩位的校服跟新的一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.34,0:14:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯 去洗衣店洗過了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.80,0:14:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大家都在呀 早安
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.60,0:14:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}早
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.58,0:14:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}早
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.62,0:14:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}幹勁十足啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.20,0:14:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是啊 幹勁滿滿的！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.77,0:14:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}領巾也換成新的了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.07,0:14:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.08,0:14:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}久美子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.59,0:14:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.35,0:14:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你的領巾…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.17,0:14:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哇 真的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.62,0:14:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}多謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.69,0:14:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒事沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.88,0:15:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我就猜可能會這樣 就多帶了一條
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.01,0:15:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}厲害吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.96,0:15:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.82,0:15:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}對吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.81,0:15:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}加油
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.23,0:15:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.74,0:15:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}久美子你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.92,0:15:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.45,0:15:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}超努力練習的吧？都流鼻血了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.48,0:15:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}在河邊也是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.92,0:15:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.65,0:15:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}之前我聽見了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.78,0:15:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}肯定沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.32,0:15:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我會全力支持的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.54,0:15:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.89,0:15:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好了 搞定
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.46,0:15:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}快點吧 還要試音吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.74,0:15:37.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.63,0:15:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}啊 久美子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.60,0:15:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.77,0:15:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}今天加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.31,0:15:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯 我會加油
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.62,0:15:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}早啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.86,0:15:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}太晚了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.84,0:15:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.96,0:15:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}慢點 慢慢來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.36,0:15:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這個可以搬上去了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.77,0:15:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.96,0:16:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}先把打擊樂器放進來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.04,0:16:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.51,0:16:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.05,0:16:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.62,0:16:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好 低音號走囉！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.35,0:16:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我來搬吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.88,0:16:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.52,0:16:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.05,0:16:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.64,0:16:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我也該從新手畢業了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.87,0:16:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.32,0:16:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}塚本
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.17,0:16:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.10,0:16:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}一定在等你…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.72,0:16:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}久美子她
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.61,0:16:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}鬆手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.36,0:16:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.20,0:16:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好重
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.92,0:16:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這可是低音號啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.98,0:16:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}遊覽車也出發了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.77,0:16:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那我們莫娜卡隊就簡單收拾一下音樂教室
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.14,0:16:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}再坐電車過去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.09,0:16:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}到了會場 就照剛才說好的行動
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.87,0:16:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要留心搬進去的順序
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.43,0:17:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這時候出差錯 會影響演奏的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.27,0:17:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大家注意點
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.50,0:17:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.56,0:17:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}莫娜卡 莫娜卡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.61,0:17:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.55,0:17:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那要來囉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.15,0:17:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}莫娜卡 Fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.73,0:17:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.80,0:17:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那什麼啊 好大
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.29,0:17:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}名為「愛」的騷擾
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.35,0:17:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.14,0:17:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}裡面好像塞著什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.64,0:17:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.55,0:17:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}啊 寫著大吉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.31,0:17:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}啊 真驚喜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.29,0:17:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真的耶 有東西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.84,0:17:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真講究
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.91,0:17:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}來 塚本的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.55,0:17:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哦 多謝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.82,0:17:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這可是特製的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.66,0:17:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}加油哦 塚本同學
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.76,0:17:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.90,0:17:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}突然叫什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.20,0:17:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.60,0:17:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哎 怎麼會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.85,0:17:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好的 我們會想辦法 先掛了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.22,0:17:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.51,0:18:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好像是把最大的鼓槌忘在社辦裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.14,0:18:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.21,0:18:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}來不及了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.01,0:18:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不行啊 學校現在好像也沒人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.93,0:18:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我去拿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.96,0:18:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}加藤
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.74,0:18:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.53,0:18:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是時間…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.95,0:18:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒問題 我用跑的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.92,0:18:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我坐後面的電車追你們
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.86,0:18:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大家先去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.95,0:18:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}加藤
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.62,0:18:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我們等你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.37,0:18:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小心點
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.66,0:18:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.49,0:18:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.75,0:18:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒問題的 她可是加藤
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.79,0:18:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}夏紀學姐為什麼會加入管樂社？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.98,0:18:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}為什麼啊…加藤呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.52,0:19:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}感覺很高雅又很帥嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.37,0:19:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}一點也不高雅
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.78,0:19:12.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}說得也是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.46,0:19:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}練習那麼嚴 跟高雅還差得遠呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.01,0:19:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但我還是很慶幸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.37,0:19:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}抱歉！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.65,0:19:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就算讓我再選一次
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.84,0:19:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大概還是會選管樂社！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.93,0:19:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}有了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.95,0:19:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好！
