Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.76,0:20:06.97,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\1c&H555254&\fn華康墨字體\frz325.6\move(442,338,456,154,0,2196)}大\N膽\N{\1c&H7F453A&}上{\1c&H555254&}\N吧{\1c&H7F453A&}\N！！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.03,0:20:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}可別小看低音號手的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.11,0:20:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}肺活量啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.93,0:20:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}加藤
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.27,0:21:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}按平時練習的來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.79,0:21:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎麼樣 沒問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.65,0:21:02.69,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你趕上了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.04,0:21:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.21,0:21:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.93,0:21:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好了 快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.27,0:21:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.73,0:21:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}辛苦你了 加藤
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.93,0:21:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒什麼 你可要加油
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.89,0:21:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}葉月？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.04,0:21:26.61,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}抱歉忘記鼓槌了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.61,0:21:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}她一路跑去拿鼓槌了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.56,0:21:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.74,0:21:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你還好吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.97,0:21:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.09,0:21:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}葉月
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.29,0:21:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小綠
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.85,0:21:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}辛苦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.12,0:21:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.48,0:21:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我說…小綠
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.22,0:21:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我很期待你完美的演奏呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.13,0:21:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}包在我身上！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.85,0:21:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}北宇治的各位 請
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.46,0:22:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}開始了
